      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span&gt;hp pool.  You will need DoN expansion to be able to use any of these features.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Guild banker is for items that you like anyone in the guild to use (few people in the guild will have the ability to flag items for other people or classes or for anyone).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Guild Tribute is intended for raid type enhanced buffs.  Contribute as you like.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In guild lobby you can have your corpse summoned anytime when you give the appropriate level summon item to one of the summoners.  Summon item (I forget the name) can be purchased depending upon the level of summoned corpse(s).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
